Dear All,
  Wish you all a very happy new year!

Just to let you all know - so that you can be better prepared -

The next ACM DEV will be in London this year in November - Marco
Zennaro and I will be the General Chairs while Elizabeth Belding and
Jay Chen will be the PC Chairs. We are currently working out plans to
make ACM DEV bigger than the previous years.

We will have the next GAIA workshop along with ACM DEV and we are keen
to have more participation from the GAIA members.

Thanks for your continued support and have a great year!

Regards

-- 
